videos.headline: Buechele delivers a strike to Granson for a TD
videos.description: SMU QB Shane Buechele drops a dime to his TE Kylen Granson for a 22-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Ahlers unleashes a 68-yard TD pass to Hatfield
videos.description: Pirates QB Holton Ahlers slings it downfield for a 68-yard touchdown to tie the game.

videos.headline: Buechele connects with Granson again for 2nd TD
videos.description: SMU QB Shane Buechele has all the time in the world in the pocket and delivers to Kylen Granson for a short touchdown.

videos.headline: Jones powers through line after big gain from Rice
videos.description: SMU's Rashee Rice comes up with a big 20-yard gain that puts the Mustangs in perfect position for RB Xavier Jones to rumble his way into the end zone.

videos.headline: ECU defender gets Mossed by Proche  on 51-yard TD
videos.description: SMU's WR James Proche climbs the ladder and brings down a big catch from Shane Buechele for a 51-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Snead comes up with an incredible catch for a 36-yard TD
videos.description: ECU QB Holton Ahlers slings one across his body down the field, and Tyler Snead comes up with a beautiful diving catch for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Byrd bobbles ball, but holds on for 45-yard ECU TD
videos.description: ECU WR Zech Byrd barely hangs on to complete a catch as he hauls in Holton Ahlers' pass for a 45-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Snead breaks tackle, turns on jets for 47-yard TD
videos.description: SMU Holton Ahlers threads the needle for Tyler Snead, who breaks the tackle and takes it 47 yards to bring the Pirates within one point.

videos.headline: Jones finds wipe-open field for 64-yard TD
videos.description: Xavier Jones bounces around defenders and then takes off for a 64-yard touchdown to put the Mustangs ahead 45-37.

videos.headline: Ahlers, Snead connect for third TD vs. SMU
videos.description: Holton Ahlers airs it out to Tyler Snead, who snags it and tumbles into the end zone for a 57-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Buechele finds Granson for third scoring connection of game
videos.description: SMU's Shane Buechele find Kylen Granson downfield and places it perfectly for a 31-yard touchdown and a 52-44 lead.
